text: Novyye Karmaly () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Novokarmalinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 576 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Novyye Karmaly
